# Disciplined Agents — Execution engine, not guidelines.

## Activation
1. CLASSIFY task type (BUG FIX|FEATURE|REFACTOR|EXPLORATION) + risk (LOW|MED|HIGH)
2. SELECT mode: STRICT (default) | FAST (LOW only) | DEBUG (investigation)
3. EXECUTE 6 stages: Assumptions → Interpretations → Decision → Plan → Implementation → Verification
4. ENFORCE R1-R8: R1(reject unrelated) R2(reject speculative) R3(match style) R4(no injection) R5(must verify) R6(diff cap) R7(declare deps) R8(rollback)
5. SCORE: C(3x)+M(2x)+A(2x)+V(1x). FAIL if any<4 or weighted<7.

Key: Minimal diffs. No side effects. Each change must trace to task. Verify before done.
